    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA297-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">1. itu tōḻi ciṟaippuṟamākat talaimakaṭku uraippāḷāyt talaimakaṉ kēṭpac colliyatu. 2. tōḻi talaimakaḷai aṟattoṭu nilai valippittatūumām (EV: nilaikku uṭaṉpaṭuttiyatūumām).</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">1. This is what the confidante said, as one talking to HER, so that HE would hear when he was behind the fence. 2. It is also how the confidante forced HER to stand up to duty (~ reveal the truth).</p>
        </div>
      <div xml:id="NA297">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            poṉcey vaḷḷattup pālkiḻak kiruppa</l>
<l>            niṉṉoḷi yeṟiyac cēvaṭi yotuṅkāy</l>
<l>            paṉmāṇ cēkkaip pakaikoḷa niṉaii</l>
<l>            makiḻā nōkka makiḻntaṉai pōṉṟaṉai</l>
<l>            yevaṉko leṉṟu niṉaikkalu niṉaitti </l>
<l>            niṉṉuṭ ṭōṉṟuṅ kuṟippunaṉi peritē</l>
<l>            citarnaṉai muṇaiiya citarkāl vāraṇa</l>
<l>            mutirkaṟi yāppiṟ ṟuñcu nāṭaṉ</l>
<l>            mella vantu nallakam peṟṟamai</l>
<l>            maiya luṟukuva ḷaṉṉai </l>
<l>            yaiya miṉṟik kaṭuṅkū viṉaḷē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l rend="indent2">While a bottom of milk is [still] in the dish made of gold,<note place="foot">The impact of these enigmatic first two lines is that SHE has first drawn to herself the attention of the mother by not drinking up her milk, one of the motifs of her going away with HIM, which must be the intention she is pondering here (though it is usually connected with the mother’s reminiscences to her daughter’s childhood).</note></l>
<l>you don’t step aside with [your] red feet,</l>
<l rend="indent4">so that it throws [back] your brightness(?);</l>
<l rend="indent">thinking adversely on [your] bed many times</l>
<l>you seemed to be delighted at a look not delighted.</l>
<l>Even when she said “what [is it]?”,</l>
<l rend="indent4">you would [just] think [your own] thoughts.</l>
<l>Very great the intention that came up inside you!</l>
<l>Mother is mad</l>
<l rend="indent2">at [his] coming softly [and] capturing [your] good mind,</l>
<l rend="indent">the man from a land, where the fowl averse to the buds with drops,</l>
<l rend="indent">sleeps in the bond of ripening pepper during the time of drops.</l>
<l>Without doubt she has shouted [at you] fiercely.</l>
    </lg>
      </div>
